</svg></span></button></div></div></div><div class="bl l"><div><div class="bk" aria-hidden="false"></div></div></div></div></header><span class="l"></span><section><div><div class="ds gv gw gx gy gz"></div><div class="ha hb hc hd he"><div class=""><h1 id="478f" class="pw-post-title hf hg hh bd hi hj hk hl hm hn ho hp hq hr hs ht hu hv hw hx hy hz ia ib ic id bi">ATMTA Sells $1.6 Million USD Worth of ATLAS and POLIS Over Last 3 Months</h1></div><p id="da03" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">What began as an investigation into a potential exploit by <a class="jc jd ge" href="https://medium.com/u/5ed69ff9cfb0?source=post_page-----30666e2359ba--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a> community members led to the public discovery that ATMTA, Inc. sold over $1.6 million dollars worth of ATLAS and POLIS over the last three months. No official reason has been given for these sales.</p><p id="e36a" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><em class="je">This article has been updated to reflect that jup.ag was the primary exchange for USDC transfers, not MEXC. The article was update to reflect links to Solscan highlighting the transaction details.</em></p><figure class="jg jh ji jj fd jk er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jl jm di jn bf jo"><div class="er es jf"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*9tBtOkfMmCa503hA.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jp jq c" width="700" height="700" loading="eager" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div></figure><h1 id="9bc5" class="jr js hh bd jt ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko bi"><strong class="ak">Reading the Blockchain</strong></h1><p id="a730" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">Star Atlas community blockchain analysts discovered on Friday that ATMTA, Inc has been selling company owned POLIS and ATLAS tokens since mid-January.</p><p id="0a06" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Blockchain analysis was conducted by Andre from <a class="jc jd ge" href="https://medium.com/u/1e2c913fa2a0?source=post_page-----30666e2359ba--------------------------------" rel="noopener" target="_blank">The Club Guild</a> with additional verification from yaawn of Bulk.</p><p id="0f04" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">The detective work began when community member Andre posed a <a class="ae ku" href="https://discord.com/channels/789226204980707409/874400139534536745/1094028169759166626" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">question</a> to the Economics channel in the Star Atlas Discord late Friday evening.</p><blockquote class="kv kw kx"><p id="25d7" class="ie if je ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ky iq ir is kz iu iv iw la iy iz ja jb ha bi">“Anyone know who B5hX2Aj8FYmdYjXQFVF1jpz7BkrdpLXgSPs92G6DFGjA is? He’s been selling 1.6 million USD worth of $atlas and $polis last 3 months” — <strong class="ig hi"><em class="hh">Andre</em></strong></p></blockquote><figure class="jg jh ji jj fd jk er es paragraph-image"><div class="er es lb"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1016/format:webp/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 1016w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 508px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1016/0*yeszcMrwELOyaKKe.png 1016w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 508px"/><img alt="" class="bf jp jq c" width="508" height="364" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div><figcaption class="lc ld et er es le lf bd b be z dx"><strong class="bd jt">Birdeye.so overview of <em class="lg">B5hX2Aj8FYmdYjXQFVF1jpz7BkrdpLXgSPs92G6DFGjA wallet activity over the past 90 days</em></strong></figcaption></figure><p id="b9f7" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Andre also noted that these token swaps were being conducted primarily on the jup.ag decentralized exchange, where tokens were ultimately swapped for USDC and transferred to Coinbase.</p><p id="faf8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><em class="je">You can view a summary of the community’s analyst work at the end of the article.</em></p><figure class="jg jh ji jj fd jk er es paragraph-image"><div role="button" tabindex="0" class="jl jm di jn bf jo"><div class="er es lh"><picture><source srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/format:webp/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px" type="image/webp"/><source data-testid="og" srcSet="https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:640/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 640w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 720w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:750/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 750w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:786/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 786w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:828/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 828w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1100/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 1100w, https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:1400/0*uXp-gaMLaAMzwvsW.png 1400w" sizes="(min-resolution: 4dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 4) and (max-width: 700px) 50vw, (min-resolution: 3dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 67vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 3) and (max-width: 700px) 65vw, (min-resolution: 2.5dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2.5) and (max-width: 700px) 80vw, (min-resolution: 2dppx) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, (-webkit-min-device-pixel-ratio: 2) and (max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px"/><img alt="" class="bf jp jq c" width="700" height="409" loading="lazy" role="presentation"/></picture></div></div><figcaption class="lc ld et er es le lf bd b be z dx">$POLIS holdings of MEXC Global</figcaption></figure><h1 id="4771" class="jr js hh bd jt ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko bi">ATMTA Sells Tokens, Official Reason Unknown</h1><p id="c3b2" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">ATMTA has yet to release an official statement regarding the sale of privately held ATLAS and POLIS tokens. During the last Star Atlas town hall that occurred on February, 3rd, CEO Michael Wagner indicated that the team would likely begin selling tokens “<em class="je">in the near future”.</em></p><blockquote class="kv kw kx"><p id="a424" class="ie if je ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ky iq ir is kz iu iv iw la iy iz ja jb ha bi">We weren’t in a position to sell any of our tokens last year, I took a strong position against that. So, at some point in the future though, it should be expected and realistic that we are going to be selling some of our tokens on a regular basis into the market as well. Our objective there is to be market neutral, we don’t want to have any impact on the market rate either up or down…there is a huge opportunity for us to capitalize on the ecosystem tokens that we hold on our balance sheet<em class="hh">. —</em><strong class="ig hi"><em class="hh"> CEO Michael Wagner on token sales</em></strong></p></blockquote><figure class="jg jh ji jj fd jk"><div class="bz dy l di"><div class="li lj l"></div></div><figcaption class="lc ld et er es le lf bd b be z dx"><em class="lg">Star Atlas Feb 3 Town Hall; comments begin at the 1:26:04 mark</em></figcaption></figure><h1 id="b313" class="jr js hh bd jt ju jv jw jx jy jz ka kb kc kd ke kf kg kh ki kj kk kl km kn ko bi">Community Sentiment on Token Sales</h1><p id="b09a" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi">In many projects, the sale of project tokens by developers can be an ominous portent. However, some in the Star Atlas community were unfazed by this revelation and viewed it in a positive light.</p><p id="2d49" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">While no official reasoning has been given by ATMTA, positive-leaning community members speculate that the token sales are a method by which ATMTA is increasing its development runway through the year. ATMTA was impacted by the <a class="ae ku" rel="noopener" href="/blockchain-biz/star-atlas-heavily-affected-by-ftx-catastrophe-ceo-remains-committed-180cf3c2f5a9">FTX collapse</a> last year, shortening its development runway by approximately half. ATMTA eventually recovered a portion of its <a class="ae ku" rel="noopener" href="/blockchain-biz/space-game-star-atlas-recovers-lost-funds-from-ftx-3d0c13f6ed83">lost funds.</a></p><p id="bbb0" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Other community members were not as reassured and viewed the selling activity in a more dismal light. Without an official statement from ATMTA, these individuals were concerned that something more nefarious was occurring.</p><p id="ef25" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Despite the sales, several individuals in the community pointed out that ATMTA would need to significantly elevate it selling rate to even come close to liquidating its entire token reserves. Others were also quick to point out that ATMTA was sacrificing its position in the Star Atlas DAO to secure revenue, a forward leaning projection for some.</p><p id="a170" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Whatever the reason, the sale of Star Atlas tokens by ATMTA will likely continue.</p></div><div class="ab cl lk ll go lm" role="separator"><span class="ln bw bk lo lp lq"></span><span class="ln bw bk lo lp lq"></span><span class="ln bw bk lo lp"></span></div><div class="ha hb hc hd he"><h1 id="2ea7" class="jr js hh bd jt ju lr jw jx jy ls ka kb kc lt ke kf kg lu ki kj kk lv km kn ko bi">Summary of Blockchain Analysis</h1><p id="7aa8" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih kp ij ik il kq in io ip kr ir is it ks iv iw ix kt iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi">Andre’s source analysis of ATMTA’s account:</strong></p><div class="lw lx ez fb ly lz"><a href="https://solscan.io/account/GgYtnDJMHQG4gpVzy2KHukSvHfFJcs1jLXASsBCQE83P" rel="noopener  ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><div class="ma ab dw"><div class="mb ab mc cl cj md"><h2 class="bd hi fi z dy me ea eb mf ed ef hg bi">Account GgYtnDJMHQG4gpVzy2KHukSvHfFJcs1jLXASsBCQE83P</h2><div class="mg l"><h3 class="bd b fi z dy me ea eb mf ed ef dx">The user-friendly and real-time update Scanning Tool for the Solana Ecosystem. Track your $SOL and Solana-related…</h3></div><div class="mh l"><p class="bd b fp z dy me ea eb mf ed ef dx">solscan.io</p></div></div><div class="mi l"><div class="mj l mk ml mm mi mn jp lz"></div></div></div></a></div><p id="fe2a" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi">Yaawn’s explanation of ATMTA’s Transactions</strong></p><p id="985f" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><em class="je">That 4zLYwzBiEK6 wallet is the team [ATMTA] and GgY is team [ATMTA] wallet as well. Yes it’s 100% team swapping POLIS and ATLAS for USDC to send to HYNeQp {ATMTA wallet].</em></p><p id="f3b7" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><em class="je">The 4zLYwz is their [ATMTA] </em><strong class="ig hi"><em class="je">deposit address for MEXC</em></strong></p><p id="b629" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi"><em class="je">Transfers to Coinbase</em></strong><em class="je">: 3ehmDUijQ4cxk8ZhqChBCs9Cyo5zHAnkwR3eUEaoVguwhDnRbr8iH8omAU3N4nbMwUfZE9ZWGNCo7UAAbNPXK54P</em></p><p id="2004" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae ku" href="https://solscan.io/tx/4ER73ekiyyZQU5mL4Wz347tfeqCcfDrENDR42v4AArjovodP6x9hEtZmyW4oetevy7z9Rt3s8J2NB6KRyXhNeExg" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><em class="je">4ER73ekiyyZQU5mL4Wz347tfeqCcfDrENDR42v4AArjovodP6x9hEtZmyW4oetevy7z9Rt3s8J2NB6KRyXhNeExg</em></a></p><p id="8538" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi"><em class="je">Transfers to HYNeQp from GgYtnD</em></strong><em class="je"> </em><a class="ae ku" href="https://solscan.io/tx/3csfPNdSMveceUvsoQr2Mivv41or4AVusWiRgMcYQ9cL9MhwmjBigC2GWRNuLkUztJz8qkkdrn6XNi2kGtCxUSfb" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><em class="je">3csfPNdSMveceUvsoQr2Mivv41or4AVusWiRgMcYQ9cL9MhwmjBigC2GWRNuLkUztJz8qkkdrn6XNi2kGtCxUSfb</em></a></p><p id="0edb" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi"><em class="je">Transfer to HYNeQp from B5hX2A</em></strong><em class="je"> </em><a class="ae ku" href="https://solscan.io/tx/62sgVW4kjshu7vHq5LnFUozn4KUne7GXw5mE8UsNXqXmfRNbHCpNUpCkhGowfxBTA6o2zWMUHXM8KasKcw6ybmSy" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank"><em class="je">62sgVW4kjshu7vHq5LnFUozn4KUne7GXw5mE8UsNXqXmfRNbHCpNUpCkhGowfxBTA6o2zWMUHXM8KasKcw6ybmSy</em></a><em class="je"> [links all the wallets there]</em></p><p id="ca85" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><em class="je">GgY is their [ATMTA’s] “active” address basically that’s where marketplace fees etc go</em></p></div><div class="ab cl lk ll go lm" role="separator"><span class="ln bw bk lo lp lq"></span><span class="ln bw bk lo lp lq"></span><span class="ln bw bk lo lp"></span></div><div class="ha hb hc hd he"><p id="137e" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi">About the Author</strong></p><p id="3199" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae ku" href="https://medium.com/u/41e0c5b141f1?source=post_page-----4922901fb224--------------------------------" rel="noopener">Krigs</a></p><p id="1215" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">is a pioneer in the world of Star Atlas, having founded The Hologram News Network — an independent meta-news organization that keeps players up to date on all developments regarding Star Atlas. An ardent supporter of emerging technologies, Krigs has been covering this game for over a year and believes passionately in their power to revolutionize our collective gaming experience.</p><p id="241b" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">Follow on Social Media:</p><p id="9f02" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae ku" href="https://open.spotify.com/show/2mxndrDW6yPfpS350ijzjt?si=ec7c717f998240d6" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Podcast</a> | <a class="ae ku" href="https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCDa-YxgNG6A9xpH1qyP0OaQ" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">YouTube</a> | <a class="ae ku" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Twitter</a> | <a class="ae ku" href="https://twitter.com/home" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Instagram</a> | <a class="ae ku" href="https://thehologram.io/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Web</a></p><p id="c91c" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><strong class="ig hi">About The Hologram</strong></p><p id="2c07" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi"><a class="ae ku" href="https://medium.com/the-hologram" rel="noopener">The Hologram</a> is Star Atlas’ first and only independent news network. Our vision is to become the most trusted source of information about Star Atlas and a voice for the whole community. Readers can expect a high standard from our reporting and staff. Our promise to you: we will not publish anything that hasn’t been thoroughly researched and based on the best facts available.</p><p id="0a02" class="pw-post-body-paragraph ie if hh ig b ih ii ij ik il im in io ip iq ir is it iu iv iw ix iy iz ja jb ha bi">The Hologram is not endorsed or paid by the <a class="ae ku" href="https://staratlas.com/" rel="noopener ugc nofollow" target="_blank">Star Atlas</a> team. Any information published by The Hologram nor its writers should be considered as informational in nature and does not constitute any financial advice.</p></div></div></section></div></div></article></div></div></div><div class="ab cl"><div class="dk bf dl dm dn do"><div class="mo mp ab gf"><div class="mg ab"><a class="mq aw al mr" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/star-atlas?source=post_page-----30666e2359ba---------------star_atlas-----------------"><div class="ms di du mt mu mv bd b be z bi mw">Star Atlas</div></a></div><div class="mg ab"><a class="mq aw al mr" rel="noopener follow" href="/tag/economics?source=post_page-----30666e2359ba---------------economics-----------------"><div class="ms di du mt mu mv bd b be z bi mw">Economics</div></a></div></div></div></div><div class="l"></div><footer class="mx my mz na nb nc nd ne nf ab q ng nh c"><div class="l ad"><div class="ab cl"><div class="dk bf dl dm dn do"><div class="ab ff ni"><div class="ab q cb"><div class="nj l"><span class="l fm nk nl e d"><div class="ab q cb"><div class="pw-multi-vote-icon di nm nn no np"><div class=""><div class="nq nr ns nt nu nv nw al nx ny nz np"><svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-label="clap"><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M11.37.83L12 3.28l.63-2.45h-1.26zM15.42 1.84l-1.18-.39-.34 2.5 1.52-2.1zM9.76 1.45l-1.19.4 1.53 2.1-.34-2.5zM20.25 11.84l-2.5-4.4a1.42 1.42 0 0 0-.93-.64.96.96 0 0 0-.75.18c-.25.19-.4.42-.45.7l.05.05 2.35 4.13c1.62 2.95 1.1 5.78-1.52 8.4l-.46.41c1-.13 1.93-.6 2.78-1.45 2.7-2.7 2.51-5.59 1.43-7.38zM12.07 9.01c-.13-.69.08-1.3.57-1.77l-2.06-2.07a1.12 1.12 0 0 0-1.56 0c-.15.15-.22.34-.27.53L12.07 9z"></path><path fill-rule="evenodd" clip-rule="evenodd" d="M14.74 8.3a1.13 1.13 0 0 0-.73-.5.67.67 0 0 0-.53.13c-.15.12-.59.46-.2 1.3l1.18 2.5a.45.45 0 0 1-.23.76.44.44 0 0 1-.48-.25L7.6 6.11a.82.82 0 1 0-1.15 1.15l3.64 3.64a.45.45 0 1 1-.63.63L5.83 7.9 4.8 6.86a.82.82 0 0 0-1.33.9c.04.1.1.18.18.26l1.02 1.